    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You shape your Chakra, sending it to a creature you have been bonded to by the Fuinjutsu: Ninjou Kan technique in order to strengthen it. The bonded creature gains a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls or a +1 dodge bonus to Defense and Reflex saves,. You can double the bonus by increasing the technique's cost to 4.<br><br>A creature cannot be affected by this technique more than once at the same time.</p>\n\n\n\n",
